net.oneandone.mork.classfile

Class MethodRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.oneandone.mork.classfile.Reference
      • net.oneandone.mork.classfile.MethodRef

  • public class MethodRef
extends Reference
    Reference of a class or interface method. I don't distinguish class and interface methods by different types - in parallel to Java's treatment of primitive types as Class objects.
